Results.ReviewText: Nescafe has always been my go to coffee and the new varieties did not disappoint! I'm usually drawn to the stronger flavour barista style coffees so I had to try this one. It's rich and full bodied yet smooth and delicious, exactly what I come to expect from Nescafe. Top marks!
Results.Title: Smooth and delicious

Results.ReviewText: It is hard to strike a balance between the convenience of instant coffee and the great taste of a coffee shop brew. Nescafe's Gold Blend Barista succeeds where many before have failed. For those looking for a quick, great tasting brew for their morning fix... look no further!
Results.Title: A no fuss instant coffee shop hit of caffeine

Results.ReviewText: I have found the perfect instant coffee in this brand. I am very fussy about my coffee and love it fresh from bean to cup, but sometimes when I am away from my coffee machine I need a good instant and I am so glad I have found one after years of searching. Well done Nescafe!
Results.Title: Lovely taste

Results.ReviewText: For me it has all the flavour of freshly ground coffee without the hassle.From the moment you peel back the silver foil seal a savour the wonderful coffee aroma to the last cup of coffee out of the tin it keeps it's freshness and taste. I wouldn't drink any other coffee now.
Results.Title: A perfect cup every time

Results.ReviewText: Decided to try this as it was something different to what I normally use and found it to be much better than the Nescafé I had bought in the past. It had a lovely warming aroma and a nice smooth warming kind of taste. Am going to buy some again as it's an enjoyable coffee
Results.Title: Lovely Aroma & Taste

Results.ReviewText: The taste of the coffee is superior to any other that i've tried in the past. It has a really deep flavour and none of the bitterness that i've found in other ones i've tried. It's the perfect way to wake up in the morning and to continue drinking throughout the day.
Results.Title: Fantastic taste

Results.ReviewText: I buy Nescafé Gold Blend Barista all the time and take it with me on holiday as can never find anything else that matches it. When I make. It for others they always compliment the great coffee I make .  Enjoy it every time and it smells wonderful - thank you Nescafe
Results.Title: Wonderful !!!!!!!!

Results.ReviewText:
We love this in our office. Great on a Monday morning when you need a pick me up after a hectic weekend. 
Or any morning when you don't have time to make fresh coffee.

Great taste and I love the tin. 

I use the empty ones as desk tidies in the office
Results.Title: Office favourite

Results.ReviewText: I bought this a few months ago and have continued to buy this blend as it has that lively fresh pot of coffee aroma to it from the second you open the container to that last cup! I also began to buy this for my work-time coffee drinking too, it is so good!
Results.Title: Our go to coffee at home or in work!

Results.ReviewText: I bought this coffee on special and I am very annoyed  I only bought one the one I am using now is nearly all gone and I will have to pay full price. This is a  great tasting coffee and good value because you only need a small spoonful for a strong cup.
Results.Title: GREAT TASTING COFFEE

Results.ReviewText: Unable to buy our regular coffee whilst away we tried this. We were not disappointed. It was much nicer than our usual coffee being rich in flavour without being overpowering and the aroma was most enticing. We have now made this coffee our one to buy.
Results.Title: Packed full of flavour and aroma.

Results.ReviewText: Being a Nespresso lover I am so happy to have found this product which is the nearest thing to perfection when you want the convenience of an instant coffee... Lots of my workmates now agree with me that this coffee really does have an amazing taste
Results.Title: Amazing taste

Results.ReviewText: I have bought this product a number of times. Most instant coffee smells and tastes very similar. This one smells tastes like freshly prepared filter coffee but without the hassle. A definite 5 star luxury coffee. Try it. You won't be disappointed
Results.Title: Real Coffee real quick

Results.ReviewText: This is the best coffee. I have recommended it to everyone i know. If you like coffee from one of those commercial overpriced chains they you will love this. It is the best coffee and only one that i can say is on par with shop bought standard.
Results.Title: The best coffee

Results.ReviewText: Nescafe Gold Blend #Barista Style' is a luxurious coffee - rich and strong, making you feel like you are enjoying a posh cafe coffee, but in the luxury of you own home and not having to spend out on the posh cafe shop prices. Great product!
Results.Title: Rich, strong coffee when you need a treat

Results.ReviewText: We have preferred Gold Blend coffees since they first became available and now the "Barista Style" particularly because we prefer coffee without milk.  It presents a fuller flavour without the after-taste that can spoil other coffees.
Results.Title: Reliably Pleasant

Results.ReviewText: This is the best coffee blend I have ever bought. The taste is superb, very smooth and flavoursome. The packaging is attractive and the product itself is excellent value for money. I will definitely be purchasing this coffee again.
Results.Title: Wonderful flavour

Results.ReviewText: We bought this coffee to try and when we did we thought the taste was much better and smoother and we felt the NASCAFE was spoiling us having the finer things in life. Who needs the lottery when you have nascafe gold in your life.
Results.Title: NASCAFE GOLD for the finer things in our life

Results.ReviewText: Recently bought this and its turned into my guilty pleasure ... I cannot start my day without a coffee anyway but honestly this starts my day and easily gets me threw to my afternoon before I need another to help finish off my day
Results.Title: Guilty pleasure

Results.ReviewText:
Can't believe that you've got the fresh coffee taste freeze dried. 
One teaspoon is ample for a strong mug. 
Good strength of flavour and the smell is just like sitting in a coffee shop. 
Really does taste like ground coffee.
Results.Title: States exactly what to expect

Results.ReviewText: Brought these a few weeks ago for when I have company and do not want to put the machine on for just 2 coffee but still want a great taste of freshly ground beans. Was very impressed with this coffee and will continue to buy.
Results.Title: Great strong smooth taste

Results.ReviewText: I bougot this product nearly 3 weeks ago and since that day I m taking coffee 2 times a day. This product has great taste and it exceeded expectation on taste wise. I'm happy to recommend this product to friends and family.
Results.Title: Great Taste

Results.ReviewText: My wife and I drink quite a lot of coffee and don't always have time to have our "filtered drink". We were always looking for an "instant" coffee with a fresh full flavour and believe this is the best one that we've tried.
Results.Title: Instant coffee with real coffee taste

Results.ReviewText: As a regular coffee drinker i changed to Barista style some time ago and I must say that the fact that our coffee machine has not been switched on for over a year speaks volumes. It really is the best by a country mile.
Results.Title: Best by far!

Results.ReviewText: I got this for a weekend treat. We've tried it black, 50/50 and 100% hot milk. All are fine for a quick cup of coffee, but I must admit I do prefer freshly ground coffee beans. But as I say if in a rush a good stand by.
Results.Title: Don't too bad

ClientResponses.Response: Thanks for taking the time to share your thoughts with us. We've no plans to bring back NESCAFÉ Parisien at the moment but we'll pass your comments to the rest of the team.

Results.ReviewText:
So disappointing - just like drinking hot water, no taste that we can detect.
Why ever did you stop doing the Parisien? I shall stick with your Alta Rica blend.  Perhaps you could revive the Parisien one in a new jar.
Results.Title: Tin looks promising

Results.ReviewText: Although more expensive, with this coffee you get what you pay for. I use mostly ground coffee but i keep a tub of Barista Style Gold Blend handy for guests and they always seem to want more than one cup of this.
Results.Title: Best of the Instant Coffee's!

Results.ReviewText: This is a great coffee. I found it very smooth compared to some other 'Barista'-style coffees and not bitter or harsh at all. I think it's tremendous quality and value-for-money. I will buy this again and again.
Results.Title: Great product!

Results.ReviewText:
To be honest I am not a Nescafe fan as I find their coffee very blend.
However I was very surprised by the rich flavour of this coffee and have been converted, however disappointed that Nescafe proved me wrong.
Results.Title: The Box was eye catching

Results.ReviewText: From my first cup Nescafe Gold Blend Barista style didn't let me down. A full-bodied brew with no bitter after taste. Warm and invigorating, guaranteed to get me going every morning. A must have in my cupboard.
Results.Title: Coffeelation!
